Title: Prawn coctail
Subtitle: A Deliciously indulgent dish
P1: An indulgent coctail of prawns and a rich coctail sauce, optionaly served with lemon
P2: The sauce consists of a delicous seasoned combo of ketchup, mayo and worchester sauce.
P3: Optionaly served with parsley or a herb of your choice
Minor_note: Contains several alergens, see alergens for details
